feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 30, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104owd1726469066691.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/owd1726469066691.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/owd1726469066691.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"owd1726469066691\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This section provides description for the logical widget ux-DataGrid\n\t\tproperties.</p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"owd1726469066691__fig_pdy_gnk_dhc\">\n<p class=\"p\">ux-DataGrid widget</p>\n<img alt=\"uxdatagrid widget preview\" class=\"image\" id=\"owd1726469066691__image_fqm_mnk_dhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/uxdatagrid1.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"owd1726469066691__table_em5_l3z_scc\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Property</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Logical widget name</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ux-DataGrid</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Maps to physical widget</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\"></code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Default definition in <code class=\"ph codeph\">[webentitywidgets]</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">ux-DataGrid=uxdatagrid</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Supported triggers</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Used for </td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">(Non) Database entity enabling the user to view the data of the\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tentity.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qrf1726470825903.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uxdatagrid</a><p>The uxdatagrid is an entity-level widget that shows tabular entity data as a set of rows and columns. The uxdatagrid allows users to quickly and easily look up values that indicate some kind of connection between different types of data, for example name of an employee in an organization and their salary, or a day of the week, or the timetable for a local swimming pool.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lzi1701171069984.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UX Widgets</a><p>Uniface UX provides a set of widgets that are implemented using the UX Widget Interface. This set is referred as UX Widgets. The sources of these widgets are available and allow changes and/or extensions to the widgets. In a default Uniface installation, you can find the sources in the &lt;install&gt;\\uniface\\webapps\\uniface\\common\\ux folder.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421664\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421664\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ux-DataGrid Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 30, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This section provides description for the logical widget ux-DataGrid properties. ux-DataGrid widget Property Description Logical widget name ux-DataGrid Maps to physical widget Default definition in [webentitywidgets] ux-DataGrid=uxdatagrid Supported triggers None Used for (Non) Database entity enabling the user to view the data of the entity. Related Links uxdatagrid The uxdatagrid is an entity-level widget that shows tabular entity data as a set of rows and columns. The uxdatagrid allows users to quickly and easily look up values that indicate some kind of connection between different types of data, for example name of an employee in an organization and their salary, or a day of the week, or the timetable for a local swimming pool. UX Widgets Uniface UX provides a set of widgets that are implemented using the UX Widget Interface. This set is referred as UX Widgets. The sources of these widgets are available and allow changes and/or extensions to the widgets. In a default Uniface installation, you can find the sources in the <install>\\uniface\\webapps\\uniface\\common\\ux folder. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}